WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.070 align:middle line:84%
>> On Awakening Mind Part
2, The Mind Unveiled.

00:00:04.070 --> 00:00:06.700 align:middle line:84%
>> The mind is
actually a duality.

00:00:06.700 --> 00:00:10.610 align:middle line:84%
It's also known as
Maya or illusion.

00:00:10.610 --> 00:00:12.530 align:middle line:90%
>> This week on Gaia.

00:00:12.530 --> 00:00:15.540 align:middle line:84%
>> Awakening is waking
up from this duality,

00:00:15.540 --> 00:00:19.386 align:middle line:84%
from the split between
witness and witnessed.

00:00:19.386 --> 00:00:23.060 align:middle line:10%
>> On Dragonfly
enLightening Talks.

00:00:23.060 --> 00:00:24.270 align:middle line:90%
>> They call it luminescence.

00:00:24.270 --> 00:00:25.070 align:middle line:90%
It's in our cells.

00:00:25.070 --> 00:00:26.880 align:middle line:84%
Every cell, they measure
it now for beauty.

00:00:26.880 --> 00:00:29.270 align:middle line:10%
But the reality is it's
actually who we are.

00:00:29.270 --> 00:00:31.700 align:middle line:84%
>> On Beyond Belief
with George Noory.

00:00:31.700 --> 00:00:35.120 align:middle line:84%
>> If we could figure out
how to open up a portal,

00:00:35.120 --> 00:00:36.510 align:middle line:90%
travel becomes easier--

00:00:36.510 --> 00:00:38.510 align:middle line:84%
the opportunities that
we could have to get from

00:00:38.510 --> 00:00:41.930 align:middle line:84%
point A to point B in
the blink of an eye.

00:00:41.930 --> 00:00:44.297 align:middle line:10%
>> On Open Minds
with Regina Meredith.

00:00:44.297 --> 00:00:45.630 align:middle line:10%
>> I have this quantum language.

00:00:45.630 --> 00:00:47.640 align:middle line:10%
I opened up a portal
and all of a sudden,

00:00:47.640 --> 00:00:49.050 align:middle line:10%
I wasn't taken into a memory.

00:00:49.050 --> 00:00:51.260 align:middle line:84%
I was taken to a
physical experience.

00:00:51.260 --> 00:00:53.148 align:middle line:90%
>> On Journeys Into the Soul.

00:00:53.148 --> 00:00:54.690 align:middle line:84%
>> One day I was
swimming in the sea,

00:00:54.690 --> 00:00:56.670 align:middle line:84%
having this
conversation with God,

00:00:56.670 --> 00:01:00.260 align:middle line:84%
and the voice in my head said,
you'll come to Malta to be

00:01:00.260 --> 00:01:03.300 align:middle line:90%
a spiritual healer.

00:01:03.300 --> 00:01:06.110 align:middle line:90%
>> Only on Gaia.

00:01:06.110 --> 00:01:07.000 align:middle line:90%